        <item>
          <title>Trump administration halts immigration applications for migrants from 19 travel-ban nations</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Trump administration is pausing immigration applications, including green cards, for people from 19 countries previously banned from travel. This decision follows the shooting of two National Guard troops in the nation's capital last week.]]></description>
